commit.message: Added open-data.europa.eu

Add two ECB specimens

These are downloaded according to the examples on the ECB website:
https://sdw-wsrest.ecb.europa.eu/help/

$ wget \
  https://sdw-wsrest.ecb.europa.eu/service/data/EXR/M.USD.EUR.SP00.A
$ wget -O structure.xml \
  --header 'authorization: Basic ZXV1c2VybmFtZTpwYXNzd29yZA=='
  https://sdw-wsrest.ecb.europa.eu/service/datastructure/ECB/ECB_EXR1
